chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, RB Salzburg \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra \u01b0u th\u1ebf qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p thua v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00c1o v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i \u1edf c\u00e1c c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u00c1o c\u00f2n \u0111ang tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u0103ng hoa v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 11 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng (t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 giao h\u1eefu). Trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 10 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG \u00c1o m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, RB Salzburg c\u0169ng kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 3 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Marco Rose \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Shkendija ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00ean RB Salzburg th\u1eeba s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1o ra 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRB Salzburg \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng th\u0103ng hoa. 9/12 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00c1o k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Shkendija ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong n\u0103m 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- \u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, RB Salzburg \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Shkendija v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ Shkendija (4-2-3-1): Zahov - Bejtulai, Adili, Musliu, Murati - Alimi, Totre - Selmani, Emini, Shefiti - Ibraimi.<br>\r\n+ RB Salzburg (4-3-1-2): Stankovic - Lainer, Pongracic, Ramalho, Ulmer - Schlager, Samassekou, Mwepu - Wolf\u00a0 - Yabo, Dabbur.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2353","checkdouble":"194440"},{"date":"09:53 14/08","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u Emery \u0111ang l\u00e0m g\u00ec v\u1edbi Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/huyen-thoai-khong-hieu-emery-dang-lam-gi-voi-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Tony Adams k\u1ecbch li\u1ec7t ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00ec nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p l\u00fd trong tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac trong th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda khi Arsenal nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i hai b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110KV\u0110 Man City ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018/19.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u1ea5t cho tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Theo \u0111\u00f3, hai t\u00e2n binh Bernd Leno v\u00e0 Lucas Torreira b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ch\u1ec9 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Emery b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/huyen-thoai-khong-hieu-emery-dang-lam-gi-voi-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Emery b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 c\u1ef1u trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Tony Adams l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng k\u1ecbch li\u1ec7t ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Emery: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n Xhaka, t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n Torreira, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ecf con nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng minh, \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ch\u00fang ta v\u00e0 t\u00f4i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh vai tr\u00f2 v\u1edbi N\u2019Golo Kante \u1edf Chelsea c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ea1i sao Leno kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong khung th\u00e0nh c\u01a1 ch\u1ee9? T\u00f4i y\u00eau qu\u00fd Cech, m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0ng th\u00f4i n\u00e0o, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi r\u1ed3i. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u1ea3 Maitland-Niles \u1edf h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i n\u1eefa, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb non n\u1edbt kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Man City? Th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, t\u00f4i t\u1edbi gi\u1edd v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u Emery \u0111ang l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u1edf Arsenal su\u1ed1t 5-6 tu\u1ea7n qua. N\u1ebfu l\u00e0 gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m th\u00ec h\u1eb3n t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t n\u00f3ng m\u1eaft v\u1edbi anh ta l\u1eafm r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\">Arsenal 0-2 Man City: B\u00ecnh m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u ch\u01b0a m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. V\u00e0 r\u00f5...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2352","checkdouble":"194441"},{"date":"10:35 14/08","title":"T\u00e2n binh Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen hay h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/chuyen-ve-naby-keita-phan-1-vua-cua-duong-pho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-siz